namnecho bharoti-i vicharvont. orvind ghox ho ddo. krixnnodhovn ghox ani svorgolta devi hancho tisro put. ddo. krixnnodhovn hannem inglix bhaxentlean unchele xikxonn ghetil'lem. ghorant to bongali bhaxa vaprinastona inglix va hindi bhaxa vaportalo. orvind ani tache don vhoddle bhav darjiling hangachea loretto konnventt skul hanga xikle.he xallent choddxe iuropi-i bhurge xiktale ani madhiom' puraiponnan inglix axil'lem. darjiling hanga don vorsa xikxonn purai zalea uprant orvindak tachea bhavondda soit inglonddak xikxonna khatir dhaddlo. thoim to ddrevett nanvanchea brittix kuttumbache dekhrekhi khal axil'lo. hea vellar tachi pirai sumar sat vorsanchi axil'li. ani ddo. krixnnodhovn hannem aplea bhurgeank bhartiom kodden kosloch sompork ievcho nhoi oxim zotnai ghetil'li. ddo. krixnnodhovn hanchi vagnnuk toxi asli, tori tankam bhartantlea brittix razvottivixim tiddok axil'li. haka lagun bhurgeponnatoch orvind ani tachi bhavondda hancher dex bhoktiche sonskar zanvk pavle. 1891 kembriz hanga 'bharoti-i mozlis' he sonsthechi thaponnuk zali, ten'na orvind te sonsthecho sekrottori zalo.

inglondd ani inglonddche rajkaronn hachevixim monant vaitt mot nirmann zata astonach orvindachea monant airolondd che svatontrotaiechea andolnacho fuddari, parnel hache vixim apulki nirmann zali. parnel haka moronn aile ten'na tannem parnelchi tust korpi ek kavio ghoddoilem. bhartantlea movall rajkaronnavixim orvindachea monant ken'nach mog nirmann zalo na. urfatte zohal bhartiamni 'lottos add ddegor' nanvachi gupt krantikarok songhottona nirmili, ten'na orvindoi te songhottnent samil zalo. he gupt songhottnechea sobhasodamni matbhuimeche svotontrotaie khatir morosor zhuzpacho soput ghetil'lo. fuddem hi songhottona lhov lhov korun kabar zali.
inglonddantlea chovda vorsanchea rabiteant orvindan inglix , lettin ani grik bhaxancher probhutv melloilem. he bhair french, ittali-ion, spenix ani jormon hea bhaxanche ginean mellovn ghetlem. avoibhaxa bongali mat taka bhartant porthun ailea uprant xikchi poddli.inglonddant astona 1890 t orvindan ai.si.es. porikxa dili. punn ghoddear bospache porikxent napas zalean to ai.si. es. zanvk xoklo na. orvindachea monantoi brittixanchi chakri korpachi itsa naxil'lich

1892 t orvindan kembrizchea kingoz kolezantlean podvi melloili. ani 1893 to bhartant ailo. boddoda sonsthanacho raza soiajirav gaikovadd hannem aplea sonsthanant revheniu khateant taka nokri dili. kaim disa uprant boddoda mohavideantolean tannem poilim french ani uprant inglix bhaxechem odheapon suru kele. kaim kall tea mohavidealoiacho to prachario legit zalo.

svotontrotaiechea andolnant vantto ghevchem nodrentlean orvindan 'vonde matorom'' nanvanchem disallem uzvaddanvk survat keli. hea disalleacho sompadok astona brittix sorkaran rajdrohacho arop dovrun tacher khottlo bhorlo. punn neaialoiant tachi nirdox mhonn mekllik zali. 1907 savn tannem rajki chollvollint nettan vantto ghenvnk survat keli. 1908 t brittix sorkaran porthun tacher rajdrohacho ani brittix samrajea add kott kel'leacho arop dovrun khottlo bhorlo. hea vellar chit'toronzon das tachem vokiloptr ghevn khottlo zhuzlo. vorsobhor ho khottlo choltalo. xevttak porthun orvindachi nirdox mhonn muktotai zali. 'kormiogi' hem inglix ani 'dhorm'' hem bongali satollem tannem choloilem.boddoda hanga astona orvindachem logn ranchi hanga sthaik zal'lea bhupalchondr hanchi dhuv mrinnalini hiche kodden 1909 vorsa zalem.

orvindache dexobhktichem ani rajkaronnachem mull tache adheatmik provrit'tint axil'lem. 1907 t gvalhercho lele nanvacho mharaxttri-i iogi taka mell'llo ani orvindache adheatmik sadhnek arombh zalo. fuddem rajkaronn ani lovkik jivit hancho purai somneas ghevn 1910 t poilim chondrnogor hanga ani uprant panddicheri hea french vosnnukamni vochun tannem axrom' ukte kele. axromache thaponnuke uprant choddant chodd vell ekantvasant ravn orvind iogsadhona korunk laglo. 15 egostt 1914 disa savn 'ario' nanvachem adheatmik vixeak ompil'lem mhoineallem tannem mira richoroddos ani pol richoroddos hea zoddpeachea polvan suru kelem.

1918 t orvindachi ghorkan'n mrinnalini, panddichiri hanga ienvnk bhair sorli, punn vattent kolkt'ta hanga infliuienzhachea duiensan tika moronn ailem. 24 nouhembor 1926 disa orvindak iogsid'dhi prapt zali ani to purai ekantvasant ranvk laglo. 'esez en do gita', 'laif ddivhain' hea sarkea gronthanchi borpavoll tannem 'ario' mhoinalleantolean keli. 'savitri' hem tache mohakavio borench namnechem asa.

